Machinery

Company Overview of Blue Bird Corporation



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Blue Bird Corporation designs, builds, manufactures, sells, and maintains school buses. It also offers buses for activity/commercial purposes, child care, general services administration, global markets, and specialty needs. In addition, the company offers bus parts, support, maintenance, and repair services. It offers its products through dealers in North America, Africa, Asia, the Caribbean, Latin America, Europe, and the Middle East. The company was formerly known as Blue Bird Body Company and changed its name to Blue Bird Corporation in 1992. The company was founded in 1927 and is based in Fort Valley, Georgia. Blue Bird Corporation operates as a subsidiary of The Traxis Group B.V.


402 Blue Bird BoulevardP.O. Box 937Fort Valley, GA 31030United StatesFounded in 1927



