HOME
Products
Business Tablets
Enterprise Tablet
ST100




Smart Tablet Computer
ST100
Popular 10.1-inch tablet that pairs sleek consumer styling with enterprise class tools and services. 
Ideal for use in retail and other customer facing situations where durability is not a requirement.



Design Features Specifications Accessories Resources 

























Sleek, lightweight design
ST100 weighs just above 700 grams (1lb 9oz) and offers enterprise computing without compromising the sleek consumer styling. 













Extended product life cycle
When purchasing a Bluebird product, you can be sure that the product will be supported for several years to come. Unlike suppliers of consumer-grade devices, Bluebird stands behind its products for years, significantly extending the product life cycle and protecting customers’ investment in the company’s products. 
Bluebird offers a 1-year warranty against manufacturer defects and a 3- or 5-year comprehensive warranty where wear and tear is also covered. 














Multiple OS support
ST100 supports multiple operating systems, including  Android 4.4, Microsoft Windows Embedded 8.1 Industry Pro, and Windows 10 IoT Enterprise. 
In addition, Bluebird can assist with customization of the operating system to enhance security, simplify deployment, and reduce support costs.













Long battery life
ST100 has an energy-efficient processor that preserves battery life to make sure it lasts the entire work shift and longer.













Scratch resistant display
ST100’s 10.1-inch multi-touch display, is protected by Corning® Gorilla® Glass 3 that is exceptionally resistant to scratches and deep chips. 










Specifications




Dimensions
254.2 x 172.4 x 9.98 mm



Weight
700g


Display
10" HD (1280 x 800)
Corning® Gorilla® Glass 3 with native damage resistance™ (NDR)


